Package: tSeriesTools
Type: Package
Title: Tools for testing for unit root and stationarizing series
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Marina Ferent-Pipas
Maintainer: Marina Ferent <marinaferent@gmail.com>
Description: The package contains functions that:
    (1) test for unit root and display type of non-stationarity based on Ayat and Burridge (2000) sequencial procedure
    (2) based on the exact type of non-stationarity identified, stationarize the series
